Device string Hardware Notes <code>"CPU"</code> Intel x86 AVX2 / AVX-512 / VNNI auto-selected <code>"GPU"</code> Intel iGPU/dGPU Needs <code>intel-opencl-icd</code> installed <code>"NPU"</code> Intel NPU Ultra/Lunar Lake laptops only <code>"AUTO"</code> Best available OpenVINO picks; falls back if first choice fails <code>"GPU.0"</code> / <code>"GPU.1"</code> Specific iGPU/dGPU Multi-GPU systems <p>In <code>OpenVINOInferencer.__init__</code> we default to <code>"CPU"</code> and only try <code>"GPU"</code> if the user explicitly asked for it and <code>core.available_devices</code> shows it:</p> <pre><code>ov_device = "CPU"
if self.device and self.device.upper() in ("GPU", "AUTO"):
    if "GPU" in core.available_devices:
        ov_device = "GPU"
    else:
        logger.info(f"Intel GPU not available, using CPU. Available: {core.available_devices}")
</code></pre>
